HEADWORD: Testiculate
<hw>Tes*tic"u*late</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[NL.
<ets>testiculatus</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <sd>(a)</sd>
<def>Shaped like a testicle, ovate and solid.</def> <sd>(b)</sd>
<def>Having two tubers resembling testicles in form, as some species of
orchis.</def>⟦br⟧
